    "causal_summary": "Add first-class sk-doc authoring support for the behavior_benchmark family: three fillable templates (index, scenario contract, baseline), an end-to-end creation guide, and a create-benchmark SKILL/README extension, so a deep-loop mode's behavior_benchmark package can be authored the way MCP promotion benchmarks already are. Templates mirror the shipped deep-alignment package and sk-doc conventions; the shared framework stays the single measurement contract.",
